932	 *         +---------+                        +--------+
933	 *         |         |  SRAM ports            |        |
934	 *         |  Logic  |----------------------->| Memory |
935	 *         | Module  |  SRAMb ports           | Module |
936	 *         |         |----------------------->|        |
